### Notes
eu_ai_act:deep_fake rdfs:comment "Ambiguous concept retained as a class because the source alternates between content and system interpretations. Source: Regulation (EU) 2024/1689; https://artificialintelligenceact.eu/ai-act-explorer/." .
eu_ai_act:model_information rdfs:comment "Modeled as a class because the source treats it as a structured information object. Source: Regulation (EU) 2024/1689; https://artificialintelligenceact.eu/ai-act-explorer/." .
eu_ai_act:article_5 rdfs:comment "Modeled as an article individual and class-like legal provision reference for prohibited practice assertions. Source: Regulation (EU) 2024/1689; https://artificialintelligenceact.eu/ai-act-explorer/." .